    examTip: "Remember that EVA's adjustments to invested capital are designed to convert accounting figures into economic realities; focus on understanding *why* each adjustment is made, not just memorizing the list.",
    memoryAid: "EVA = Economic Value Added = NOPAT - (WACC * Invested Capital). Think: EVA helps EVALUATE if the company is truly adding VALUE.",
