      2: "Why option C is WRONG - The pooling of interests method is no longer permitted under U.S. GAAP. ASC 805 exclusively uses the acquisition method for business combinations.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - While the lower of cost or market principle applies to inventory, it is not the standard for valuing assets acquired in a business combination. ASC 805 requires fair value measurement.",
