    question: "Cascade Corp. implements zero-based budgeting (ZBB). The marketing department submits three decision packages: Package A ($200K — essential brand maintenance), Package B ($150K — digital advertising expansion), and Package C ($100K — trade show program). If the budget allocation is $380,000 total, which packages are funded?",
