    explanation: "5-factor DuPont: ROE = (NI/EBT) × (EBT/EBIT) × (EBIT/Sales) × (Sales/Assets) × (Assets/Equity). Tax burden, interest burden, operating margin, asset turnover, leverage. Pinpoints performance drivers.",
