    question: "A factory has two overhead cost pools: Machine Setups ($180,000, driven by number of setups) and Quality Inspections ($120,000, driven by inspection hours). Product A requires 40 setups and 200 inspection hours. Product B requires 60 setups and 100 inspection hours. Total setups are 100 and total inspection hours are 300. Under ABC, what is overhead allocated to Product A?",
