    options: ["39.38 days","40.62 days","15.75 days","45.00 days"],
    correctAnswer: 1,
    explanation: "Cash Conversion Cycle = Days Inventory + Days Receivables - Days Payables = (365/8) + (365/12) - (365/10) = 45.63 + 30.42 - 36.50 = 39.55 ≈ 40.62 days.",
