    examTip: "Remember the formula: Cash Conversion Cycle = Days Inventory Outstanding + Days Sales Outstanding - Days Payable Outstanding; make sure to use 365 days for annual calculations.",
    memoryAid: "CCC = Inventory + Receivables - Payables (I Really Pay attention to Cash)",
