    examTip: "Remember that the perpetuity growth model is based on sustainable, long-term growth, so focus on rates that reflect this, and always ensure the discount rate is higher than the growth rate.",
    memoryAid: "Growth rate must be LESS than discount rate, or you'll have a MESS!",
    reference: "DCF Valuation",
