    examTip: "Remember the formula: Cash Conversion Cycle = DIO + DSO - DPO; think of it as how long cash is 'stuck' in inventory and receivables, offset by payment delays.",
    memoryAid: "CCC = Buy (DIO) + Sell (DSO) - Pay (DPO)",
    reference: "Working Capital Analysis",
