    options: ["EuroSub's functional currency is the Euro because its costs are primarily denominated in Euros.","EuroSub's functional currency is the US dollar because all of its sales are to GlobalTech in US dollars and its operations are highly integrated with the parent company.","EuroSub's functional currency is the US dollar because the ultimate sales of the final product occur in the US market.","EuroSub's functional currency is the Euro because it is located in Germany and operates independently."],
