    examTip: "Pay close attention to the intercompany transactions and the degree of integration between the foreign subsidiary and the parent company. Significant integration and transactions in the parent's currency often point to the parent's currency as the functional currency.",
    memoryAid: "ISFE: Indicators, Sales, Financing, Expenses (to remember factors influencing functional currency)",
    reference: "ASC 830",
