    explanation: "Ongoing monitoring of KPIs and data analytics, coupled with management review and follow-up, is the most effective monitoring activity. This approach allows for continuous assessment of control effectiveness, timely identification of deficiencies, and prompt corrective action. This aligns with the COSO Framework's emphasis on ongoing evaluations as an integral part of monitoring activities.",
