    examTip: "Pay attention to words like \"ongoing\" and \"separate evaluations\" when answering questions about monitoring activities within the COSO framework. Look for answers that emphasize independent verification and continuous improvement.",
    memoryAid: "REMEMBER: Monitoring is the M in CRIME (Control Environment, Risk Assessment, Information and Communication, Monitoring Activities, Existing Control Activities). Monitoring is about ensuring the other CRIME components are working effectively.",
