    options: ["Issue an unqualified opinion, provided management acknowledges the uncertainties surrounding the new technology in the notes to the prospective financial statements.","Issue a qualified opinion, disclosing the inconsistencies in the underlying assumptions related to sales growth and gross profit margins in the report.","Issue an adverse opinion, because the unrealistic assumptions render the forecast misleading and not fairly presented.","Withdraw from the engagement, because the unrealistic assumptions are pervasive and undermine the credibility of the prospective financial statements, and indicate management may lack integrity."],
