    examTip: "Remember that the times interest earned ratio focuses on interest coverage, not overall debt coverage. Focus on EBIT and interest expense when calculating this ratio.",
    memoryAid: "TIE = EBIT / Interest Expense (Think: 'TIE your EBIT to your Interest')",
    reference: "COSO Framework (for understanding the importance of monitoring debt obligations)",
