    question: "XYZ Company uses a standard costing system. The standard cost for direct materials is $5 per pound. During the month, XYZ purchased 12,000 pounds of direct materials for $57,000. XYZ used 11,000 pounds of these materials in production. What is XYZ's direct material purchase price variance?",
