    options: ["Immediately liquidate the company's assets and file for bankruptcy, as the ratios indicate imminent failure.","Develop and implement a detailed action plan to improve liquidity, solvency, and profitability, closely monitoring key performance indicators and regularly updating cash flow projections.","Obtain a bridge loan to improve the current ratio and delay any significant operational changes until the industry recovers.","Disclose the going concern uncertainty in the financial statements but take no immediate action, as the prospective financial information is inherently uncertain."],
