    question: "Tech Solutions Inc. recently implemented a new cloud-based ERP system. The company's internal audit department is evaluating the effectiveness of the system's internal controls. Which of the following monitoring activities would provide the MOST persuasive evidence regarding the ongoing effectiveness of access controls over sensitive financial data within the ERP system?",
    options: ["Reviewing the system access logs quarterly to identify any unauthorized access attempts and documenting the investigation and resolution of any incidents.","Conducting a self-assessment survey annually asking employees whether they have experienced any issues with the ERP system's access controls.","Performing a walkthrough of the ERP system with the IT manager to understand the system's access control features.","Comparing the list of employees with active ERP system access to the HR department's list of current employees annually."],
