    options: ["Reviewing the system access log for the past month to identify any users whose access privileges do not align with their current job responsibilities.","Periodically testing the effectiveness of the system's password complexity requirements by attempting to create weak passwords.","Conducting a survey of department managers to gather their opinions on the overall security of the new ERP system.","Comparing the total number of customer records in the new ERP system to the number of customer records in the legacy system."],
    correctAnswer: 0,
