    options: ["Increase net sales by 10% while holding all other expenses constant.","Reduce cost of goods sold by 5% while holding all other expenses constant.","Decrease operating expenses by 15% while holding all other expenses constant.","Issue additional debt to repurchase outstanding shares, increasing the debt-to-equity ratio by 0.5."],
