    options: ["The accountants must independently verify the validity of the 20% sales growth assumption by performing detailed market research and competitor analysis.","The accountants should express an opinion on whether the 20% sales growth assumption is likely to be achieved, based on their professional judgment.","The accountants should determine that the responsible party (Apex's management) has a reasonable basis for the 20% sales growth assumption.","The accountants should perform a sensitivity analysis to determine the impact on the pro forma financial statements if the sales growth is only 10% instead of 20%."],
