    examTip: "Remember to calculate the flexible budget based on the *actual* activity level. Pay close attention to whether the variance is favorable (F) or unfavorable (U).",
    memoryAid: "Favorable means good (actual costs are lower), Unfavorable means bad (actual costs are higher).",
