    options: ["Establishing a baseline of key performance indicators (KPIs) related to the redesigned processes and regularly comparing actual results to the baseline, investigating significant variances and reporting to management.","Conducting a one-time review of the system's configuration settings to ensure they align with the company's policies and procedures.","Relying solely on the ERP system's built-in audit trails to detect errors or irregularities.","Implementing a hotline for employees to report suspected fraud or unethical behavior, and investigating all reported incidents."],
