    options: ["Increase the sales department's monthly sales targets to incentivize greater efficiency.","Implement a formal process for documenting and reviewing all credit hold overrides, including justification and approval by a senior executive independent of the sales department.","Reduce the credit department's staff to streamline the credit review process and minimize delays.","Eliminate the credit hold policy altogether to avoid hindering sales and improve customer satisfaction."],
