    options: ["GlobalTech should disclose the $5 million negative impact on revenue and the $2 million negative impact on net income in the MD&A. It should also quantify the impact on segments if material.","GlobalTech is only required to disclose the impact on net income ($2 million) in the MD&A, as this is the most relevant measure of profitability.","GlobalTech is not required to disclose the impact, as foreign currency fluctuations are a normal part of international business and are reflected in the financial statements.","GlobalTech should disclose the $5 million negative impact on revenue, but only if the total revenue reduction from all factors (including currency) exceeds 10% of the previous year's revenue."],
