    options: ["The functional currency is the U.S. dollar. EuroSubsidiary must remeasure its financial statements into U.S. dollars, and no further translation is required for consolidation.","The functional currency is the Euro. EuroSubsidiary must remeasure its financial statements into U.S. dollars, then translate to the reporting currency for consolidation.","The functional currency is the Euro. EuroSubsidiary must translate its financial statements into U.S. dollars for consolidation.","The functional currency is the U.S. dollar. EuroSubsidiary must translate its financial statements into U.S. dollars for consolidation."],
