    examTip: "Carefully analyze the key factors influencing the functional currency determination: sales currency, expense currency, intercompany transactions, financing, and interrelationship. One factor may not be determinative; consider all aspects.",
    memoryAid: "FACTORS: F-inancing, A-utonomy, C-osts, T-ransactions (intercompany), O-perations, R-evenue, S-ensitivity to exchange rates.",
