    options: ["Recognize a loss of $750,000 and disclose the event in the notes to the financial statements.","Disclose the event in the notes to the financial statements only.","Adjust the December 31, Year 1, accounts receivable balance by $750,000 and recognize a loss of $750,000.","Adjust the December 31, Year 1, accounts receivable balance by $750,000 and disclose the event in the notes to the financial statements."],
