    examTip: "Pay close attention to relationships involving key management personnel (officers and board members) and their close family members. Control is a key indicator of a related party.",
    memoryAid: "COIN: Control, Ownership, Influence, Near Family. These are key indicators of related party relationships.",
    reference: "ASC 850-10-50-1",
