    options: ["TechForward should disclose the extent to which its reported results of operations and financial condition are subject to material risks due to currency fluctuations and provide a discussion of the nature of its exposure, including strategies to mitigate this risk if they exist.","TechForward only needs to disclose the total amount of foreign currency transaction gains and losses recognized during the year in the footnotes to the financial statements, as this is sufficient disclosure under US GAAP.","TechForward is only required to disclose the impact of foreign currency fluctuations if the fluctuations resulted in a net gain for the company.","TechForward is not required to disclose anything in the MD&A regarding foreign currency risk, as this is already addressed by the requirement to translate foreign currency financial statements."],
    correctAnswer: 0,
