    subtopic: "Segment Reporting",
    difficulty: "easy",
    skillLevel: "Application",
    question: "Apex Corp. has the following operating segments: Alpha, Beta, Gamma, and Delta. Segment revenues are Alpha: $30 million, Beta: $25 million, Gamma: $20 million, and Delta: $15 million. What is the revenue threshold that an operating segment must exceed to be considered a reportable segment?",
