    examTip: "Remember to calculate the threshold based on the combined amounts of ALL operating segments before comparing individual segment data.",
    memoryAid: "10% RAP (Revenue, Assets, Profit/Loss) - remember the 10% thresholds for revenue, assets, and profit/loss to determine reportable segments.",
    reference: "ASC 280-10-50-12",
