    options: ["Adjust the December 31, Year 1, accounts receivable balance and disclose the event in the notes to the financial statements.","Disclose the event in the notes to the financial statements only.","Write off the $1,200,000 receivable in Year 2 and no disclosure is necessary.","Adjust the December 31, Year 1, accounts receivable balance only; no disclosure is necessary."],
