    options: ["Gamma Corp is not required to discuss the CTA loss in the MD&A because it is a non-cash item and does not directly impact cash flow from operations.","Gamma Corp should disclose the CTA loss and its impact on the reported net loss, including a discussion of the underlying reasons for the currency fluctuation and its potential future impact on the company's financial performance.","Gamma Corp should only disclose the CTA loss if it is considered a material event under ASC 280, Segment Reporting.","Gamma Corp is only required to disclose the CTA loss in the MD&A if it has hedged its foreign currency exposure using derivative instruments as per ASC 815, Derivatives and Hedging."],
