    options: ["A statement that the company does not believe foreign currency fluctuations have a material impact on its results of operations, as the functional currency of the subsidiary is the U.S. dollar.","A discussion of the extent to which the company's reported revenue and net income increased due to the appreciation of Country X's currency against the U.S. dollar.","A detailed breakdown of all foreign currency gains and losses, including those from hedging activities, in accordance with ASC 815.","A statement that the company uses the direct method of cash flow reporting for all foreign subsidiaries."],
