    options: ["ABC Corp. cannot elect the fair value option for its available-for-sale debt securities because it also holds an equity method investment.","ABC Corp. can elect the fair value option for its available-for-sale debt securities, and the equity method investment in XYZ Inc. is not impacted.","ABC Corp. must also elect the fair value option for its equity method investment in XYZ Inc. if it chooses to apply the fair value option to its debt securities.","ABC Corp. can elect the fair value option for its equity method investment in XYZ Inc. only if XYZ Inc. also applies the fair value option to its own financial instruments."],
