    question: "A U.S. publicly traded company, Beta Corp, prepares its financial statements in accordance with U.S. GAAP. Beta Corp.'s Form 10-K includes the following disclosures: a roll-forward of its defined benefit pension plan assets, a description of its significant accounting policies, and a detailed explanation of its derivative instruments, including qualitative disclosures about how derivatives are used to manage risk. Which of these disclosures require block text tagging in the Inline XBRL (iXBRL) filing?",
