    options: ["ABC Company must disclose the nature of the relationship between ABC Company and XYZ Company, the description of the transaction, the dollar amount of the transactions, and any amounts due from or to the related party.","ABC Company does not need to disclose this transaction because the terms were consistent with market rates.","ABC Company only needs to disclose the dollar amount of the transaction if it exceeds 10% of ABC Company's total sales.","ABC Company only needs to disclose the transaction if the brother of the CEO is also a member of ABC Company's board of directors."],
