    options: ["Omega's MD&A is adequate because it disclosed the impact of foreign currency translation on revenue, satisfying the requirements of Regulation S-K.","Omega's MD&A is inadequate because it failed to disclose the risks associated with future exchange rate fluctuations, a key element of Regulation S-K.","Omega's MD&A is adequate because the impact of foreign currency translation is already reflected in the financial statements prepared in accordance with ASC 830.","Omega's MD&A is inadequate because it did not disclose the specific amount of Euro-denominated revenue, as required by Regulation S-X."],
