    options: ["Remeasure Sol S.A.'s financial statements into U.S. dollars using the temporal method, with gains or losses included in current income.","Translate Sol S.A.'s financial statements into U.S. dollars using the current rate method, with gains or losses reported in other comprehensive income (OCI).","Remeasure Sol S.A.'s financial statements into U.S. dollars using the current rate method, with gains or losses included in current income.","Translate Sol S.A.'s financial statements into U.S. dollars using the temporal method, with gains or losses reported in other comprehensive income (OCI)."],
