    question: "A manufacturing company, Apex Industries, is facing increased competition from overseas manufacturers. As a result, Apex's market share has declined by 15% in the last year, and projections suggest a further decline of 10% in the next year if no action is taken. After a thorough risk assessment, management has identified this competitive pressure as a significant threat to the company's profitability and long-term viability. Apex is considering various risk responses. Which of the following risk responses would be the MOST appropriate if the company decides to reduce the probability and impact of the risk?",
