    options: ["Perform a sensitivity analysis to assess the impact of changes in key assumptions, such as sales growth and market share, and disclose the potential range of outcomes.","Obtain a compilation report from an independent CPA to provide assurance that the forecast is free from material misstatement.","Limit the forecast to only three years to reduce the uncertainty associated with long-term projections.","Use only historical data and eliminate any forward-looking assumptions to increase the reliability of the forecast."],
